Package: compensation-analytics
Title: Compensation Analytics Dashboard
Version: 1.0.0
Date: 2025-06-23
Author: Tamara Adokeme
Maintainer: analytics@example.com
Description: Production Shiny dashboard for physician compensation analysis with 
  role-based authentication, automated ETL in R and SQL, parameterized Quarto 
  reports, variance analysis, and Docker deployment. Supports PostgreSQL and 
  SQL Server via ODBC. Falls back to sample data when no database is configured.
License: MIT
Imports:
